FILE: docs-site/docs/en/features/communication.md
1:# Communication, Tickets and Help
2:
3:Communication features cover customer support, operational announcements, system alerts and delivery status.
4:
5:## User Features
6:
7:| Feature | Description |
8:| --- | --- |
9:| Tickets | Submit issues, upload attachments, read replies and close tickets. |
10:| Inbox | Read system messages, billing reminders and resource alerts. |
11:| Help center | Read help articles maintained by administrators. |
12:| Popup announcements | Receive maintenance and important operation notices. |
13:
14:## Admin Features
15:
16:- View, filter, reply to and close tickets.
17:- Manage help articles.
18:- Publish announcements and broadcasts.
19:- Configure notification channels.
20:- Review delivery logs and failure reasons.
21:
22:## Delivery Channels
23:
24:- Inbox messages for default in-app notifications.
25:- SMTP for email verification, ticket reminders and system mail.
26:- Telegram for admin alerts, user binding and critical events.
27:- Lsky for ticket images or attachment workflows.
28:
29:## Risks
30:
31:- Ticket attachments must enforce size, type and permission checks.
32:- Notification failures must not block core billing or delivery operations.
33:- Telegram webhook URLs and tokens must remain secret.
34:- SMTP and Lsky secrets must be redacted from logs.
